{"tid":2161791,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"分化分化，泛民架空民意就唔係分化？","createTime":"2020-08-17T18:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T18:08:53.000Z","uid":103521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"27f009c4fef2d19b275904609debe35e5de52b87","tid":2161791,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T18:08:53.000Z","msg":"唔理民意就開左會先，拒絕見初選勝出者<br />\n我地忍佢地就叫唔分化，咁佢地唔聽就唔係分化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔分化原來係指要就曬泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泛民過往污點班班，忍左佢地成場運動<br />\n依家佢地自己都唔撚出聲明講會入去反抗到底<br />\n而有人唔信服就叫我地玩分化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">同埋唔係總辭，係非法留任呀屌</span></span></strong>"}]}